text:
Mutton Soup at Sunday F&B coffee shop. AMK locals favorite. Take number first and pay only when you collect the food.
Highly recommend for those who love to eat mutton soup with herbs. Usual waiting time is around 20 to 30 mins. But worth waiting as the soup is very delicious. Close at 5pm.

Newly renovated in May 2023.

Kopi c ti lok is excellent. Strong coffee taste and not acidic. Good food here as well, eg. nasi lemak, fried carrot cakes, mutton soup etc.

Newly renovated Hawker that provides good food options. Was here for breakfast and had a great selection of dim sum, including old school homemade carrot cake and glutinous rice. Their chilli was especially great!

Worst.. very stuck-up owner. They accept call in for reservation n kept telling those that walk in to wait. I been there for 1hr plus never see them serve any walk in n jus wait for those who call to collect.
Didn't try the food even i was told is nice.
I won't support such attitude hawker.

It a nice place to enjoy a meal with friends and family
Got lot of sits available
